performance on handheld devices is non-negotiable.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1330\" data-end=\"1613\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1330\" data-end=\"1425\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1332\" data-end=\"1425\"><strong data-start=\"1332\" data-end=\"1361\">Progressive image loading<\/strong> and lazy loading techniques to keep mobile performance snappy<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1426\" data-end=\"1548\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1428\" data-end=\"1548\"><strong data-start=\"1428\" data-end=\"1447\">AMP-ready pages<\/strong> and <strong data-start=\"1452\" data-end=\"1471\">CDN integration<\/strong> (such as Cloudflare) to deliver fast-loading pages even on slower networks<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1549\" data-end=\"1613\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1551\" data-end=\"1613\">Optimised themes and minimal code bloat to reduce bounce rates<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1615\" data-end=\"1711\">Whether you&#8217;re targeting Nairobi or remote counties, your site will load quickly and look sharp.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1743\">SEO-Optimised Architecture<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1745\" data-end=\"1822\">We design your store with search visibility in mind \u2014 not as an afterthought.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1824\" data-end=\"2227\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1824\" data-end=\"1896\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1826\" data-end=\"1896\"><strong data-start=\"1826\" data-end=\"1861\">Clean, crawlable URL structures<\/strong> for categories and product pages<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1989\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1989\"><strong data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1932\">Breadcrumbs and schema markup<\/strong> to improve indexing and display rich results in Google<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1990\" data-end=\"2059\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2059\"><strong data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2021\">Fully op