and upsell offers<\/strong> to increase average order value<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3654\" data-end=\"3855\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3656\" data-end=\"3855\">Seamless integration with <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/google-ads-services-and-ppc-in-kenya\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"3682\" data-end=\"3752\">Google Ads<\/a>, <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/top-seo-services-in-kenya\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"3754\" data-end=\"3824\">SEO<\/a>, and email marketing campaigns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3857\" data-end=\"3926\">We don\u2019t just build your store \u2014 we help you sell more, consistently.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"\" data-start=\"186\" data-end=\"219\">Which Platform Should You Use?<\/h2>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"221\" data-end=\"505\">The right platform is the foundation of a successful e-commerce store. At Aminifu Digital, we guide you through platform selection based on your goals, technical needs, and long-term growth plans. Below is a breakdown of the most popular platforms used in Kenya \u2014 and when to choose each.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"507\" data-end=\"522\">WooCommerce<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"524\" data-end=\"599\">WooCommerce is ideal for businesses that want full control and flexibility.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"601\" data-end=\"962\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"601\" data-end=\"710\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"710\">Perfect for <strong data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"643\">content-heavy e-commerce<\/strong>, where blogs, downloads, or gated content sit alongside products<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"795\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"713\" data-end=\"795\">Built on WordPress, allowing seamless integration with your existing site or CMS<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"873\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"798\" data-end=\"873\">Highly customisable checkout flows, shipping logic, and promotional tools<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"962\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"876\" data-end=\"962\">Excellent SEO performance with full control over metadata, schema, and page structures<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1163\">If you&#8217;re planning to invest in content marketing or need a unique blend of content and commerce, WooCommerce is a strong contender.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1176\">Shopify<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1266\">Shopify is fast, secure, and easy to launch \u2014 a great choice for product-led businesses.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1268\" data-end=\"1567\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1268\" data-end=\"1347\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1347\">All-in-one platform with hosting, SSL, backups, and updates managed for you<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1348\" data-end=\"1416\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1350\" data-end=\"1416\">Easy to set up and scale, even with minimal technical experience<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1505\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1419\" data-end=\"1505\">Ideal for businesses focused purely on product sales with fewer custom content needs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1506\" data-end=\"1567\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1508\" data-end=\"1567\">Excellent for startups and SMEs launching their first store<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1569\" data-end=\"1679\">However, Shopify has monthly subscription fees and some feature limitations compared to open-source platforms.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1698\">Other Options<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1700\" data-end=\"1759\">For unique or enterprise-level requirements, we also offer:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1761\" data-end=\"2059\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1761\" data-end=\"1892\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1892\"><strong data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1786\">Headless e-commerce<\/strong> setups using a CMS frontend (e.g., WordPress or Sanity) with a custom back-end (Laravel, Node.js, etc.)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1893\" data-end=\"1968\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1895\" data-end=\"1968\"><strong data-start=\"1895\" data-end=\"1906\">Magento<\/strong> for large enterprise-level inventory and multi-store setups<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1969\" data-end=\"2059\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1971\" data-end=\"2059\">API-driven platforms designed for integrations with ERP systems or NGO procurement tools<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2061\" data-end=\"2152\">These options are ideal for businesses with highly specific workflows or integration needs.<\/p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"2154\" data-end=\"2157\" \/>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2159\" data-end=\"2191\">Platform Comparison Table<\/h3>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto contain-inline-size\">\n<table data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"3586\">\n<thead data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"2346\">\n<tr data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"2346\">\n<th data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"2226\">Feature<\/th>\n<th data-start=\"2226\" data-end=\"2267\">WooCommerce<\/th>\n<th data-start=\"2267\" data-end=\"2307\">Shopify<\/th>\n<th data-start=\"2307\" data-end=\"2346\">Custom\/Headless<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody data-start=\"2502\" data-end=\"3586\">\n<tr data-start=\"2502\" data-end=\"2656\">\n<td>Hosting<\/td>\n<td>Self-hosted<\/td>\n<td>Included<\/td>\n<td>Self-hosted or cloud-hosted<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"2657\" data-end=\"2811\">\n<td>Initial Setup Time<\/td>\n<td>Moderate<\/td>\n<td>Fast<\/td>\n<td>Long<\/td>\n<\/