om the discovery phase, we plan your site\u2019s structure and interface:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1163\" data-end=\"1428\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1163\" data-end=\"1229\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1229\">Logical <strong data-start=\"1173\" data-end=\"1195\">category hierarchy<\/strong> and intuitive product filtering<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1296\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1296\">Wireframes for <strong data-start=\"1247\" data-end=\"1294\">homepage, product pages, and checkout flows<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1364\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1364\">Mobile-first layouts prioritising ease of use and fast browsing<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1365\" data-end=\"1428\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1428\">Trust indicators (e.g. payment icons, delivery info, reviews)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1514\">We ensure your customers can find products quickly \u2014 and feel confident to purchase.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1516\" data-end=\"1543\">3. Build &amp; Integrations<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1545\" data-end=\"1616\">With the design approved, we begin development and system integrations:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1618\" data-end=\"1876\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1618\" data-end=\"1661\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1620\" data-end=\"1661\">Setup of your chosen platform and theme<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1725\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1725\"><strong data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1683\">Product uploads<\/strong>, attributes, inventory management rules<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1726\" data-end=\"1801\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1728\" data-end=\"1801\">Integration with <strong data-start=\"1745\" data-end=\"1763\">local payments<\/strong> (e.g. M-Pesa, PesaPal, Flutte