esting &amp; Launch<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2519\" data-end=\"2585\">We put every element through a rigorous quality assurance process:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2587\" data-end=\"2775\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2587\" data-end=\"2628\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2589\" data-end=\"2628\">Cross-device and cross-browser checks<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2629\" data-end=\"2670\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2670\">Cart, coupon, and checkout flow tests<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2671\" data-end=\"2715\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2673\" data-end=\"2715\">Mobile usability and performance reviews<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2716\" data-end=\"2775\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2718\" data-end=\"2775\">SSL configuration, firewall setup, and speed optimisation<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2777\" data-end=\"2860\">Once approved, we move to a soft launch with final reviews before going fully live.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2862\" data-end=\"2895\">6. Training &amp; Ongoing Support<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2897\" data-end=\"2951\">Your team is not left behind after launch. We provide:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2953\" data-end=\"3320\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2953\" data-end=\"2999\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2955\" data-end=\"2999\">Onboarding sessions and video walkthroughs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3000\" data-end=\"3070\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3002\" data-end=\"3070\">Documentation for product updates, order fulfilment, and reporting<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"3071\" data-end=\"3261\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3073\" data-end=\"3261\">Access to optional <a href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/website-maintenance-services-in-kenya\/\">Website Maintenance<\/a> and <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/seo-packages-an-pricing-in-kenya\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopene