-first design with structured categories and clear CTAs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"868\" data-end=\"922\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"870\" data-end=\"922\">Integration with M-Pesa and local delivery partner<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"923\" data-end=\"970\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"925\" data-end=\"970\">Rich product content, schema, and on-page SEO<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"972\" data-end=\"1002\"><strong data-start=\"972\" data-end=\"1000\">Results (first 90 days):<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1003\" data-end=\"1103\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1003\" data-end=\"1027\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1005\" data-end=\"1027\">Bounce rate \u2193 by 41%<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1056\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1056\">Organic traffic \u2191 by 63%<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1057\" data-end=\"1103\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1059\" data-end=\"1103\">Customer quote requests via website \u2191 by 55%<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"214\" data-end=\"229\">The Ithira Store<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"230\" data-end=\"461\"><strong data-start=\"230\" data-end=\"243\">Industry:<\/strong> African Fashion &amp; Retail<br data-start=\"268\" data-end=\"271\" \/><strong data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"284\">Platform:<\/strong> WooCommerce<br data-start=\"296\" data-end=\"299\" \/><strong data-start=\"299\" data-end=\"316\">Website Goal:<\/strong> Build a fast, mobile-first online store that showcases the richness of African fashion while supporting nationwide delivery and online payments.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"482\"><strong data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"480\">Our Solution:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"970\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"626\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"485\" data-end=\"626\">Developed a WooCommerce-powered e-commerce site with a clean, elega